<p>
  Makes the channel private. Private channels appear in the channel list but with the name shown as "Prv" to non-members, hiding the actual channel name. Mutually exclusive with +s (secret).
</p>
<.help_h4 icon={:icon_terminal}>Usage</.help_h4>
<pre>/mode +p    — Make channel private
/mode -p    — Remove private mode</pre>
<.help_h4 icon={:icon_link}>See Also</.help_h4>
<p><.help_link topic="mode-s">Secret (+s)</.help_link></p>
